Laparoscopic therapy of organic hyperinsulinism. The results of laparoscopic treatment were analyzed in 9 patients, suffering pancreatic insulinoma, in the clinic in 2008-2012 yrs. Tumoral enucleation was performed in 6 patients, distal pancreatic resection--in 3. In 1 (11.1%) patient postoperative external pancreatic fistula have developed. All the patients are alive. Laparoscopic treatment of the patients, suffering insulinoma is effective and secure.